CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, October 12, 1946, pg. 18 reads: Younger Set Celebration - The younger set had a gala-time at the birthday party given in honor of little Charlene Hall of Mulberry Way, Oct. 3. The guest of honor (center, in front of the cake) celebrated her fifth birthday. - Harris photo."
TitMainTitle: Boys and girls standing behind Charlene Hall with two tiered cake, for her fifth birthday party, in domestic interior
